reviewText: This video shows you a lot of what you need to know to decide if you want to go to San Francisco or not. Well done, and very helpful. Will make you want to go there. (I bought it to remember my first trip there- didn't have a video camera then, duh! Don't ask me what I was thinking.) Anyway if you're planning to go to San Francisco get it.
This i a little handy video if you are going somewhere and needed more info about the place. doesn't have everyplace, but what does.  you'll like what you see.
